NAME
    RT-Extension-DebugTimers - Add detailed timers to debug performance

DESCRIPTION
    This extension provides timers for when a request takes longer than an
    allotted value.

RT VERSION
    Works with RT 4.4

INSTALLATION
    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make install
        May need root permissions

    Edit your /opt/rt4/etc/RT_SiteConfig.pm
        If you are using RT 4.2 or greater, add this line:

            Plugin('RT::Extension::DebugTimers');

    Clear your mason cache
            rm -rf /opt/rt4/var/mason_data/obj

    Restart your webserver

CONFIGURATION
    Specificy the threshold at which any request equalling or surpassing
    should be logged in seconds: Default value for loggging is any request
    that takes longer than 50 seconds.

         Set($LogRequestThreshold, 20);

